Days of year for non-leap years

Source: R/doyNonLeap.r
doyNonLeap.Rd

Data frame of days of year for each month in a non-leap year

Usage

doyNonLeap

Format

An object of class 'data.frame'.

Examples

data(doyNonLeap)
doyNonLeap
